node.text: The first board in our Artist Series features some of Yelland's most memorable photos taken at San Francisco’s iconic “Embarcadero” skate plaza, also known as "EMB". So, we asked Yelland to add his artwork to DC's Every Man's Board, also known as the EMB. With the 90s-era EMB skate photos and the skate-inspired deck feel of the EMB, this collab perfectly celebrates the shared heritage of skateboarding and snowboarding. Check the link in bio to learn more.
